  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nSometime ago, we introduced bug into unseen messages counter functionality, so the counter is not maintained between app restarts. This is super confusing, as you can log in, receive bunch of messages for some chat, stop the app before opening it (for example you have to turn off the phone for some reason, battery dies, etc.) and upon starting the app again, nothing in UI hints to the fact that you have new messages which in some chat.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug",
